name: Ketter Yaaran
content:
Ketter Yaaran was a Human male pirate who lived on Naboo during the time of the Galactic Civil War. Following the Battle of Yavin in 0 BBY, he frequented the cantina in the city of Kaadara. While there, Yaaran once supplied the whereabouts of a pirate bunker in the Gallo Mountains to a spacer interested in rescuing kidnapped nobles.
Ketter Yaaran was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Ketter Yaaran was added to the game with the "Publish 1" update, released on August 3, 2003.
